    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Construction of 15 semi-permanent health posts, repair of 1 health post, construction of 1 pre-fab PHCC and 1 DHO office\r\n\r\nProvision of surgical consummables, drugs and equipment to public health facilities, as per one of the most urgent needs identify by the DHO.\r\n\r\nProvision of direct primary health care assistance to most remote affected communities through deployment of mobile medical teams.\r\n\r\nProvision of sexual and reproductive health (SRH) services through deployment of mobile medical teams.\r\n\r\nProvision of psychosocial support to affected population.\r\n\r\nImplement a surveillance system for epidemic diseases in mobile clinics and participate in the establishment of the EWARN\r\n\r\nRapid response to potential outbreak alerts\r\n\r\nCarry out health and hygiene awareness sessions in communities"
      },
      "ne": null
